frameDefinitions: An Entity possesses a Value for a certain Attribute which is extreme when compared to the values either of other entities or to values of the same Entity at other points of time.
Criteria exist that identify a particular Subset of a Group of things into members and non-members.
The Focal_feature is defined in relation to a Landmark_feature, either as a particular part, or as an immediately bordering entity.
An Agent changes a Patient's ability to resist literal or figurative attack.
This frame is about Items in the state of occupying a certain Rank within a hierarchy.
A Subpart of a Time_period is picked out.
